                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BOHN</hi>. As far as we at present know I have lost nearly 115<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., but as many of the nobility are out of town, we shall not know till the spring, The prisoner has kept company above his rank in life, and has a good voice for singing, which has led him into company and been his ruin.</p>
